name: Iasa, The Traitor Of Jawa Canyon
Lore: 'While on a trip, King Kalit entrusted his credits, sandcrawler and mate to his friend Iasa. When Kalit returned, one was spent, one was sold and the other was missing.',
Text: 'Deploys only on Tatooine. When firing any Jawa weapon, subtracts 3 from target''s defense value. When playing Dune Sea Sabacc, may subtract 1 from or add 1 to your total.',
